<h4><span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>NOTICE: As required by the State of Arizona, Sedona Charter School campus will be closed through the end of this school year to support efforts to slow the spread of COVID-19.  During this time, teaching staff are delivering remote instructional programming to our students. Parents, please check email for updates.</em></span></h4>
